We used generalized additive mixed models (GAMM81) to explore the climate effects on NPP values in each population (86 analyses in total). This approach is based on modelling of NPPgpbt as a function of tree ages and sizes, and explanatory climate variables. The fitted common garden by population GAMMs took on the form:5NPPgpbt=sgpbAge+∑b=13βgpbTotalCgpbt+∑c=112βgpcClimgct+ZgpbBgpb+νgpb+εgpbt\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
